    "text": "\u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb2\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0b9a\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf\u0bc7\u0bcd\u0bc7\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd, \u0baa\u0bae\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bb2\u0ba3\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bb3 \u0bc7\u0bb0\u0baf\u0bb0\u0b95\u0bb2 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bae\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b95\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd.",
    "fonts": [
      "Kavivanar-Regular"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      229.91,
      194.68,
      247.69
    ],
    "text": "\u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b8a\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bc7\u0bcd \u0bc7\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1",
    "fonts": [
      "Kavivanar-Regular"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      262.22,
      529.57,
      293.84
    ],
    "text": "Woman and Child Killed in Bus\u2013Three-Wheeler Collision \u2013 Payagala Police Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      308.32,
      536.49,
      349.2
    ],
    "text": "A woman and a child were killed in a head-on collision between a passenger bus and a three-wheeler that occurred on the morning of 2 July 2026 in the Katukurunda area along the Galle\u2013Colombo Main Road, within the Payagala Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      363.64,
      524.57,
      404.52
    ],
    "text": "The three-wheeler was travelling from Beruwala towards Kalutara, while the passenger bus was travelling in the opposite direction from Colombo to Matara, when the collision occurred.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      419.1,
      541.72,
      473.78
    ],
    "text": "A 60-year-old woman and a 13-year-old boy, who were travelling in the rear seat of the three-wheeler, died at the scene. The three-wheeler driver and another woman travelling in the rear seat sustained serious injuries and were admitted to Nagoda General Hospital, Kalutara, for treatment.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      488.34,
      318.79,
      501.62
    ],
    "text": "The deceased were residents of Kalutara South.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      516.06,
      493.18,
      529.34
    ],
    "text": "The driver of the passenger bus has been arrested in connection with the incident.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      543.9,
      415.99,
      557.18
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being conducted by the Payagala Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
